<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>312</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. &quot;Lalpa hatna leh A thilhih theihna mang un!
 A thu dik achun dettak in ding un&quot;
 Kidona phuol lauhum ah bittak in hun pui ina,
 Lalpa minin na galteu zo unla.

[V2]
 Ding detun, thudik di'n,
 Lal thupiek zawpa guolzo zel di'n;
 Lalpa lopina dingin A thu a guolzo dingin,
 Lalpa hatna achun ding det un!

[V3]
 2. Lalpa hatna leh A thilhih theihna mang un!
 Dogal lau a kinunghei ngeilo di'n;
 Thudik na panpih u chun na kawmah ding zing ina,
 Amah hatna mangin masuon zel un.

[V4]
 3. Lalpa hatna leh A thilhih theihna mang un!
 A thutiem haw zuou ngeilo ding ahi;
 Na khut changlam chuh tu'n a thudik na panpih sungcheng,
 Amah na gin chun gal zo zel inla.</lyrics>
<title>&quot;BE YE STRONG IN THE LORD&quot;</title>
</song>